# ============================================================
# points-mall-frontend-base — Environment Variables Reference
# This is a build-only component library (no runtime server).
# These variables are only needed during the `pnpm build` step (Rollup).
# ============================================================

# No runtime environment variables required.
# Build tooling (Rollup) picks up NODE_ENV automatically from the shell.
# NODE_ENV=production is set by CI during `pnpm build`.
